<h2>Step 5: Add Schema Markup for Local Businesses</h2>
<p>Schema markup is structured data that tells search engines and AI systems exactly what your business does. Without it, AI models have to guess. With it, they get clean, machine-readable facts.</p>
<p>Think of schema as your business card for AI. It lists your name, address, services, hours, reviews, and more in a format machines understand instantly.</p>
<p><strong>Required schema types for local AI visibility:</strong></p>
<pre><code class="language-json">&#123;
  &quot;@context&quot;: &quot;https://schema.org&quot;,
  &quot;@type&quot;: &quot;LocalBusiness&quot;,
  &quot;name&quot;: &quot;Your Business Name&quot;,
  &quot;address&quot;: &#123;
    &quot;@type&quot;: &quot;PostalAddress&quot;,
    &quot;streetAddress&quot;: &quot;123 Main St&quot;,
    &quot;addressLocality&quot;: &quot;Your City&quot;,
    &quot;addressRegion&quot;: &quot;State&quot;,
    &quot;postalCode&quot;: &quot;12345&quot;
  &#125;,
  &quot;telephone&quot;: &quot;+1-555-555-5555&quot;,
  &quot;url&quot;: &quot;https://yourbusiness.com&quot;,
  &quot;openingHours&quot;: &quot;Mo-Fr 09:00-17:00&quot;,
  &quot;aggregateRating&quot;: &#123;
    &quot;@type&quot;: &quot;AggregateRating&quot;,
    &quot;ratingValue&quot;: &quot;4.8&quot;,
    &quot;reviewCount&quot;: &quot;156&quot;
  &#125;
&#125;
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Specifically:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>[ ] Add LocalBusiness schema to your homepage</li>
<li>[ ] Include Service schema on each service page</li>
<li>[ ] Add FAQ schema to FAQ pages and blog posts</li>
<li>[ ] Use Review schema for testimonial pages</li>
<li>[ ] Test with Google's Rich Results Test tool</li>
<li>[ ] Validate with Schema.org validator</li>
</ul>
<p>The <a href="/blog/local-business-schema/">local business schema guide</a> covers every property and sub-type. Use the most specific type available. "Plumber" is better than "LocalBusiness." "Dentist" is better than "MedicalBusiness."</p>
<p><strong>Why this step matters:</strong> Schema tells AI assistants what you do. Reviews tell them if you are trusted. Conversational content tells them how to phrase you as an answer. Schema is the foundation layer.</p>
<p>Read the full <a href="/blog/structured-data-guide/">structured data guide</a> for implementation details beyond local business types.</p>
