<h2>Step 7: Build Brand Mentions and Authority Signals</h2>
<p>Here is a data point that changes everything: <a href="https://www.growthunhinged.com/p/get-recommended-by-chatgpt">brand mentions correlate 3x more with AI visibility</a> than backlinks do.</p>
<p>Traditional SEO prioritizes links. AI search prioritizes mentions. A business name that appears across news articles, Reddit threads, industry publications, and local media gets recommended. One that only appears on its own website does not.</p>
<p><strong>High-impact mention sources:</strong></p>
<ul>
