<li><strong>Reddit</strong>. Genuine participation in local and industry subreddits</li>
<li><strong>Industry publications</strong>. Guest posts, expert quotes, case studies</li>
<li><strong>Podcast appearances</strong>. Transcripts become crawlable content</li>
<li><strong>Awards and lists</strong> ,  "Best of" lists, industry rankings, chamber awards</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Specifically:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>[ ] Submit to local "Best of" lists and awards programs</li>
<li>[ ] Pitch local media for business features and expert commentary</li>
<li>[ ] Participate genuinely on Reddit in relevant subreddits</li>
<li>[ ] Seek guest posting on industry blogs and local publications</li>
<li>[ ] Sponsor local events that generate media coverage</li>
<li>[ ] Get listed on authoritative industry directories like Clutch or G2</li>
