<p><a href="/blog/brand-mentions-vs-backlinks/">Brand mentions work differently than backlinks</a> for AI visibility. A mention without a link still counts. ChatGPT reads content. It does not follow links. The mention itself is the signal.</p>
<p><strong>Why this step matters:</strong> AI models build confidence through consensus. When multiple independent sources mention your business positively, ChatGPT treats you as a safe recommendation. Without mentions, you are invisible.</p>
<p>The exception: brand mentions on low-quality or spammy sites can hurt more than help. Focus on reputable sources. Quality over quantity applies here too.</p>
